@startuml
title UC-06 Submit Assignment (Sequence)
participant User
participant WebApp
participant AssignmentService
participant Storage
participant DB
participant NotificationService
participant Instructor

User -> WebApp: open assignment page & upload file
WebApp -> Storage: uploadFile(file)
Storage --> WebApp: fileUrl
WebApp -> AssignmentService: submitAssignment(userId, assignmentId, fileUrl, content)
AssignmentService -> DB: INSERT submission(status=SUBMITTED)
DB --> AssignmentService: submissionId
AssignmentService -> NotificationService: notifyInstructor(submission)
NotificationService -> Instructor: in-app/email
AssignmentService --> WebApp: success
WebApp --> User: submission confirmed
@enduml
